'''Anthony DeMaria Labs''', also referred to as '''ADL''', is a small manufacturer of audio equipment specializing in [[vacuum tube]] based pieces, although not exclusively. Their products are used by a wide variety of artists in both live performance and studio applications, and are used by such artists as [[Jimmy Buffett]] and [[Bootsy Collins]].

